  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>on An Unknown Planet </strong></h2><br>A spaceship crash-lands, and a small yellow robot plummets to the ground.<br>It awakens and appears to be functioning properly, able to move around.<br>Seems like it's time to explore this land,<br>to see if it can find any other companions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Linear Levels</h2>Players must eliminate all enemies in each level to progress to the next.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/4e53684d9590f177828f73c92c54a06e.poster.avif?t=1690798597\" width=610 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/4e53684d9590f177828f73c92c54a06e.webm?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/4e53684d9590f177828f73c92c54a06e.mp4?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill Utilization</h2>Make good use of the energy collected from defeating enemies to take down stronger foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/f1b182f0f1fae4a59a796481899b8ca2.poster.avif?t=1690798597\" width=610 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/f1b182f0f1fae4a59a796481899b8ca2.webm?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/f1b182f0f1fae4a59a796481899b8ca2.mp4?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Swapping</h2>Discover different types of weapons throughout the levels to further advance your progress.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/63feb2acaa8aa4a38c4c8a31bcdbb82d.poster.avif?t=1690798597\" width=610 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/63feb2acaa8aa4a38c4c8a31bcdbb82d.webm?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/63feb2acaa8aa4a38c4c8a31bcdbb82d.mp4?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Agile Evasion</h2>Master the art of evasive maneuvers to effectively dodge enemy attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/cfec6d4cfa221f0bf89b089dfccaa279.poster.avif?t=1690798597\" width=610 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/cfec6d4cfa221f0bf89b089dfccaa279.webm?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/cfec6d4cfa221f0bf89b089dfccaa279.mp4?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controller Support</h2>Play with a keyboard and mouse or use a controller for a more immersive gaming experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/dc12a3c9b72acde46319536518696abb.poster.avif?t=1690798597\" width=610 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2502750/extras/dc12a3c9b72acde46319536518696abb.webm?t=1690798597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
